    • Method Detail

      • prepareCommit

        List<CommitMessage> prepareCommit(boolean waitCompaction,
                                  long commitIdentifier)
                           throws Exception
        Prepare commit for TableCommit. Collect incremental files for this write.
        Parameters:
        waitCompaction - whether to wait for the end of the background compaction.
        commitIdentifier - Committed transaction ID, can start from 0. If there are multiple commits, please increment this ID.
        Throws:
        Exception
        See Also:
        StreamTableCommit.commit(long, java.util.List<org.apache.paimon.table.sink.CommitMessage>)
